<p>We are 70T in debt after unfunded liabilities.  We print money that has no backing.  We send aid to anyone with a pulse.  Unemployment is through the roof.  Fiscal conservatism is something we have not seen. </p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78388510,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3797169&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;20092412&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;taylo019&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c78388510" title="Link to this comment">#14</a> - Mon Aug 19, 2013 3:44 PM EDT</span><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody child " id="c78388787"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78388787,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;ericwilde&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Eric Wilde&quot;}"></div><a name="star34"></a><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="#star35" class="noborder star"><img src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_star.gif" width="16" height="16" alt="" title="Jump To Next Highly Rated Comment" /></a><a href="http://ericwilde.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://ericwilde.newsvine.com/">Eric Wilde</a></div></div><div id="commentText_78388787" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Nor is it something we need.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78388787,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3797169&quot;,&quot;contentI