nt" /></a><a href="http://elsquire.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://elsquire.newsvine.com/">Chris-1638442</a></div></div><div id="commentText_78389145" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>This way back to the stone age !!!!!! Rick Perry leads the way !</p></p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78389145,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3797169&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;20092412&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;elsquire&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">5 votes</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c78389145" title="Link to this comment">#22</a> - Mon Aug 19, 2013 4:07 PM EDT</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c78389183"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78389183,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;solidlogic&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;solidlogic&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://solidlogic.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://solidlogic.newsvine.com/">solidlogic</a></div></div><div id="commentText_78389183" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Yeah, Texans are smart aren't they.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78389183,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3797169&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;20092412&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;solidlogic&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">3 votes</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c78389183" title="Link to this comment">#23</a> - Mon Aug 19, 2013 4:09 PM EDT</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c78389195"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78389195,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-guylauten&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Guy Lauten&quot;}"></div><a name="star49"></a><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="#star50" class="noborder star"><img src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_star.gif" width="16" height="16" alt="" title="Jump To Next Highly Rated Comment" /></a><a href="http://fb-guylauten.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=nullCF07EFE9-8A56-19E8-72B5-4123FCA5509E.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://fb-guylauten.newsvine.com/">Guy Lauten</a></div></div><div id="commentText_78389195" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Might I point out that paving roads uses asphalt and oil, both of which are Petroleum Products.  So the Big Oil bastards make money coming and going, even if they DO pave the roads.  Just not as much money as if they don't.  Nice.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78389195,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3797169&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;20092412&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-guylauten&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">5 votes</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c78389195" title="Link to this comment">#24</a> - Mon Aug 19, 2013 4:09 PM EDT</span><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody child " id="c78391781"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78391781,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;miracle&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Miracle&quot;}"></div><a name="star50"></a><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="#star51" class="noborder star"><img src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_star.gif" width="16" height="16" alt="" title="Jump To Next Highly Rated Comment" /></a><a href="http://miracle.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=miracleEB60B15A-1B73-210D-C05D-B595BA54649A.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://miracle.newsvine.com/">Miracle</a></div></div><div id="commentText_78391781" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Hadn't thought of that. Do you know what another name for asphalt is? Bitumen. Perhaps they're figuring that when Keystone XL gets linked up they can sneak in in the middle of the night and tap into it to pave the gravel.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78391781,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3797169&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;20092412&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;miracle&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">5 votes</div></li></ul></div><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c78391781" title="Link to this comment">#24.1</a> - Mon Aug 19, 2013 5:59 PM EDT</span></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody child " id="c78392407"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:78392407,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-guylauten&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Guy Lauten&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://fb-guylauten.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=nullCF07EFE9-8A56-19E8-72B5-4123FCA5509E.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://fb-guylauten.newsvine.com/">Guy Lauten</a></div></div><div id="commentText_78392407" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>You can even take it a step further:</p>
<p>Tires that run consistently on gravel don't last as long as tires that run on asphalt.  So the locals would be buying more tires than they have in the past.  The tire manufacturers are one of the biggest users of... wait for it... Petroleum Products.</p>
